  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个HealthTech系统的诊断支付流程图。核心是从LabAnalyzer开始，经过EMR同步，再到DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。LabAnalyzer是起点，先同步到EMR，然后进入诊断引擎。这里EMR_Sync会出现两次吗？我看后面还有判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，EMR_Sync既是处理节点也是判断节点。第一次是同步操作，第二次D节点要做支付方式的判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主线：A到B到C，然后C连到菱形D。D这里分出QRIS和Tunai两条支路对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "QRIS",
        "Tunai"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。QRIS那条走到PatientRecords，Tunai那条要回到DiagnosticEngine做离线处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QRIS",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Tunai",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。E是PatientRecords，F是DiagnosticEngine。不过E后面还有个G也是PatientRecords，这是同一个模块吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "G是PatientRecords的确认环节，相当于二次校验。然后H节点要做Ya/Tidak的判断，决定诊断流程分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G",
        "H",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Ya",
        "Tidak"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "理解了。那H分出I和J，都是连到DiagnosticEngine？这两个分支有什么区别？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H",
        "I",
        "J",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Ya走正常诊断路径，Tidak走异常处理路径，但最终都汇聚到DiagnosticEngine的不同处理逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ya",
        "Tidak",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，H的菱形画好了，Ya连I，Tidak连J。现在Tunai那条支路F后面是K，又回到了LabAnalyzer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "F",
        "K",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，现金支付需要重新采样，所以K回到LabAnalyzer，然后K还要连到HIPAA_Vault做数据归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "K",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "L是HIPAA_Vault，已经加上去了。我检查一下整体结构，发现D节点的标签可能需要调整——现在写的是EMR_Sync，但它是判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "L",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "你说得对，D虽然是EMR_Sync，但作为判断节点应该突出支付选择。不过按我们系统命名规范，保持EMR_Sync也可以，重点是QRIS和Tunai标签要清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "QRIS",
        "Tunai"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，标签保留。我再看一下，E到G都是PatientRecords，这里会不会有循环？E输出到G，G再判断H。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "G",
        "H",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不是循环，E是记录创建，G是记录确认，H是确认结果的判断。这是三步递进，不是闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "E",
        "G",
        "H"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，三步递进。那I和J虽然都连到DiagnosticEngine，但要在注释里区分处理逻辑吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "I",
        "J",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "暂时不用注释，保持图简洁。不过我突然想到，Tunai支路的K到L，LabAnalyzer的数据直接进HIPAA_Vault合规吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "K",
        "L",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "按流程图是这样设计的。需要我调整吗？比如K先回DiagnosticEngine再进Vault？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "K",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用调整，现金支路是离线模式，LabAnalyzer直接归档符合HIPAA要求。保持现有结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "K",
        "L",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的。我再核对一遍所有连接：A-B-C-D，D分QRIS到E-G-H，H分Ya到I、Tidak到J，D分Tunai到F-K-L。K还连回A吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "H",
        "I",
        "J",
        "K",
        "L"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "K不连A，K只连L。重新采样是人工操作，系统流程到L就结束了。你把K到A的线去掉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "K",
        "A",
        "L"
