    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "节点数是对的，但H的判断标签是Ya和Tidak，不是Yes/No，这是印尼语要求，别改成英文。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "H",
