    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "放心，Ya和Tidak都保留着。D那边的QRIS和Tunai也是印尼语。整个图符合本地化要求。",
